race.comment: NOT SORRY (1) broke a string of placings finishing in the money two on end before a last start fifth (22.47) at Warrnambool. Has a good record at this journey. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. STAR FURY (2) is worth forgiving for his last effort when sixth (23.18) at Warragul over 400m. Has a strong record from box 2, including two wins. Bold showing expected. PAW LINDEN (5) goes very well here starting 15 times for five wins and six minors. In the money last time at this track (23.55) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 4.5 lengths third. Looks one of the chances. GIZMO'S GIRL (4) hit the frame latest (25.61) when third at Shepparton in a Grade 5. Has two wins already from this draw.
